title: 2014–15 Newcastle Jets FC season
text:
The 2014–15 <a href="Newcastle%20Jets%20FC">Newcastle Jets FC</a> season was the club's 14th season since its establishment in 2000. The club participated in the <a href="A-League">A-League</a> for the 10th time and the <a href="FFA%20Cup">FFA Cup</a> for the first time.
